# KNN Classifier on Iris Dataset

This project demonstrates a simple K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN) classifier using the Iris dataset.

## Project Structure
- data_preprocessing.py : Load and normalize dataset
- knn_model.py          : Train KNN model
- evaluation.py         : Evaluate with accuracy and confusion matrix
- visualization.py      : Visualize decision boundaries (PCA reduced)
- main.py               : Runs the complete workflow

## How to Run
1. Install dependencies:
   pip install pandas scikit-learn matplotlib

2. Run the project:
   python main.py
